thread.title: skyfitness

author: skyfitness
title: skyfitness
text: I have been using Fabletics since it first came out! The only negative response I would give it is the prices seem to be increasing more and more. The monthly fee is $49.99 however no outfits are really priced that anymore so I end up having to pay an additional $10+ each month to purchase something. That has deterred me from keeping it monthly and skipping several months at atime.
